## Failure Initiator Classification

`determineFailureInitiator(context)` maps failure type to the party responsible:

| FailureType | Initiator |
|---|---|
| WITHDRAWAL | `context.userRole` (BUYER or SELLER — whoever withdrew) |
| TIMEOUT | SYSTEM |
| FINAL_OFFER_REJECTED | Opposite of `finalOfferBy` (the party who rejected) |
| DECLINE | Invoking user's role |

This is stored in `NegotiationFailure.initiatedBy` (`FailureInitiator` enum: BUYER / SELLER / SYSTEM).

